In India also we have the same problem.

00:39:38.662 --> 00:39:46.882
But that's a very different type.  I mean it is not regarded... You see, because it is not an organised religion, so I can wipe it out better, but it is organised here.

00:39:46.882 --> 00:39:56.827
The Seven Day Adventist, these another horrible Pentecostals, they are organised, they are accepted by law. They are doing all these things here through law!

00:39:56.857 --> 00:40:03.190
Mother, don't you think when they give you a sense
of being guilty in Christianity and Catholic Church,

00:40:03.190 --> 00:40:06.750
they're wanting at the same
time to increase their power?

00:40:06.750 --> 00:40:09.250
Of course! It's a play! It's a play!

00:40:09.250 --> 00:40:13.540
But only an intelligent
man can see that's true.

