00:40:22.449 --> 00:40:24.949
these people have also brainwashed you.

00:40:24.949 --> 00:40:27.449
In India, also they do the
same thing - brainwashing!

00:40:29.349 --> 00:40:31.849
They have done all kinds of brainwashing,

00:40:31.849 --> 00:40:38.859
but the only difference is this, that
the Western religions are all organised.

00:40:38.896 --> 00:40:41.396
So when they are organised they become firm

00:40:41.396 --> 00:40:47.466
and they have much more power than
a religion which is disorganised.

00:40:47.494 --> 00:40:49.994
You can hit them better!

00:40:49.994 --> 00:40:55.556
Now the priest here is so much respected! In India a
priest is not respected so much. Ask him, he is a Brahmin!

00:40:57.806 --> 00:41:00.306
You see if a priest comes into
your house we do not respect him.

00:41:00.306 --> 00:41:06.037
You see, he takes money, we know he takes money. We do
not respect him the way here the priest is respected.

00:41:06.053 --> 00:41:12.168
Because it is organised. They have made their
norms and things by church, making some respect.

00:41:13.381 --> 00:41:21.476
What is terrible they gave the religion: and during the Middle Age they give to the Western countries knowledge.

00:41:21.486 --> 00:41:22.866
religion and knowledge.

00:41:22.892 --> 00:41:26.286
They had incredible power.

00:41:26.318 --> 00:41:27.396
That's it!

00:41:27.402 --> 00:41:31.028
Because through the knowledge they
wanted to introduce the religion.

00:41:31.056 --> 00:41:33.556
And afterwards religion became to be knowledge.

00:41:35.366 --> 00:41:37.066
So the vicious circle starts.

00:41:37.066 --> 00:41:41.196
So you must decide it and you must give
up your misidentifications, first of all.

00:41:41.213 --> 00:41:45.833
Because all your diseases come
from your identifications.

00:41:45.839 --> 00:41:51.793
Alright? Say now you are Greek. Now Greeks also have
certain misidentifications, quite a lot of them.

00:41:51.835 --> 00:41:52.503
Many!

00:41:53.243 --> 00:41:58.283
So once you start becoming a Sahaja
Yogi or a universal personality,

00:41:58.283 --> 00:42:02.223
you just dissipate.  You do not pamper.

00:42:02.217 --> 00:42:04.883
But if you are a real Greek,

00:42:04.917 --> 00:42:06.083
I never did.

00:42:06.080 --> 00:42:06.563
I know that.

00:42:06.563 --> 00:42:14.033
But if you are a real Greek, then you must tell all the other
Greeks also that, "This is what it is!" If you really love them.

00:42:14.097 --> 00:42:17.353
I will be really please to say that to my aunts.

00:42:19.963 --> 00:42:23.752
Your Aunt, I am not so much worried,
because that's an age now, they are gone.

00:42:23.796 --> 00:42:26.062
But what about the future that's coming up.

00:42:26.062 --> 00:42:31.932
Now the people who belong to such organised
religions, as they have, which has happened in India;

00:42:31.979 --> 00:42:34.744
(Unclear)

