in the same way it is going to happen here also, that they
are not going to believe in any religions whatsoever.

00:42:40.813 --> 00:42:45.853
The other side has started as you
said! They don't  believe in any God.

00:42:47.933 --> 00:42:49.713
I don't know what they need to find out.

