Ha?

00:42:50.103 --> 00:42:54.868
I don't really know what they need to find out.

00:42:54.909 --> 00:43:00.548
Nothing! You see, it's just a swing from one extreme
to another extreme. It's just extreme, that's all.

00:43:00.548 --> 00:43:03.048
There is no direction, there's no guidance.

00:43:03.048 --> 00:43:08.889
It's just a swing from believing into too
much, fanaticism, to another is non- belief!

00:43:08.918 --> 00:43:15.759
Or Sahaja Yoga is not like that at
