00:43:15.804 --> 00:43:19.975
so from one extreme and to another
extreme, they go just automatically.

00:43:20.016 --> 00:43:22.516
I mean it is absolutely inevitable.

00:43:24.407 --> 00:43:26.907
You have to stop in the centre.

00:43:26.907 --> 00:43:31.951
And those who are stopping must
grow, so they engulf all that.

00:43:32.012 --> 00:43:35.231
This is what I'm trying to tell you.  Alright?

00:43:36.884 --> 00:43:42.171
And then you'll start seeing them, then
you will know how horrible they are.

00:43:42.971 --> 00:43:44.059
It's very painful Mother.

00:43:44.059 --> 00:43:47.759
It's very painful to see how
horrible they are, it's true.

00:43:47.776 --> 00:43:49.699
We have to, of course, cure them.

00:43:49.726 --> 00:43:53.929
but first we should be alright, all of us
and we should pull all these things together.

00:43:53.929 --> 00:44:00.325
I don't know Mother, I've noticed that one of the way
that the negativity works is that it attacks people

00:44:00.338 --> 00:44:08.055
and then it makes you feel sorry for them and then it sucks all your energy, so that you have no chance to do any work for Sahaja Yoga.

00:44:08.099 --> 00:44:10.599
Like Rustom had this problem before,

00:44:10.599 --> 00:44:12.189
he was over sympathetic.

00:44:12.229 --> 00:44:17.159
If you have sympathies…if you see the meaning
’sympathy’ – it means ‘sharing pathos’.

00:44:17.159 --> 00:44:20.449
You share their pathos isn’t it!

00:44:20.502 --> 00:44:26.662
So this is also there. And now why, you see why I have
said this is that you have, in these Western countries,

00:44:26.755 --> 00:44:30.732
you have seen the aggression of your forefathers
so you are taking to the other courses.

00:44:30.732 --> 00:44:34.122
You are over-sympathetic.

00:44:34.162 --> 00:44:38.432
And that thing is going to
tell against you, absolutely.

00:44:39.569 --> 00:44:41.812
There is nothing to sympathise.

00:44:41.812 --> 00:44:46.912
There is to be so strong, that you
just solve the problems like that.

00:44:46.959 --> 00:44:49.459
Sitting down here you should
be able to solve the problem.

00:44:50.791 --> 00:44:52.451
So develop your powers.

00:44:52.451 --> 00:44:56.461
Alright Simon? That’s what it is.
You must develop your powers.

00:44:56.501 --> 00:45:04.324
And how will you develop them is by becoming
silent and silent within and seeing for yourself.

00:45:04.364 --> 00:45:06.864
You have to just assume!

00:45:06.894 --> 00:45:09.054
You have powers already.

00:45:09.054 --> 00:45:12.264
You have been enriched by all the Adi Shakti.

00:45:12.289 --> 00:45:14.789
Everything has been done for you.

00:45:14.789 --> 00:45:19.571
You’ve got it. You are already
empowered. Just use that.

00:45:23.248 --> 00:45:26.891
Can you doubt that you are not empowered?

00:45:30.518 --> 00:45:35.177
You already have got powers and also
most of you know what is to be done.

00:45:38.807 --> 00:45:42.397
You know what is this power to be used for.

00:45:42.447 --> 00:45:44.947
You have the knowledge as well.

00:45:47.709 --> 00:45:51.667
But only thing is to assume it! You have to assume.

00:45:51.783 --> 00:45:53.883
We need the wisdom as well.

00:45:53.883 --> 00:45:57.413
You have! You don’t need Maria.

00:45:57.413 --> 00:46:01.793
You have a lot of it. Only thing
is don’t sympathise with them.

00:46:01.863 --> 00:46:06.433
Just don’t worry about them.
They are foolish people.

00:46:06.510 --> 00:46:09.010
This is what I have been doing all the time.

00:46:09.010 --> 00:46:15.780
That’s not proper. You don’t waste your energy on
that, that’s why you have thinned down so much.

00:46:17.730 --> 00:46:21.630
There’s a saying in Urdu, “Kazidli
bidli ka shayed kya deshakte”

00:46:21.630 --> 00:46:25.270
they say, “Priest, why are you so sick?
Because you are worried about the whole world”!

00:46:25.317 --> 00:46:27.956
(Break in recording.)

00:46:29.649 --> 00:46:35.330
It’s only one second you need.
You just say, “Go away all of you!

00:46:35.370 --> 00:46:36.546
Go away!

00:46:41.743 --> 00:46:47.407
So, you see for... we had an example
of that in Bombay, in Delhi.

00:46:47.407 --> 00:46:50.796
We had those Ramkrishna
mission people. Just tell them!

00:46:52.586 --> 00:46:58.886
There was a lady who had cancer from the same
ashram and she said, “Why? I was doing upkar

00:46:58.880 --> 00:47:02.806
I was helping others. I was looking after them.”

00:47:02.851 --> 00:47:05.811
I said, “Then why did you get cancer?”

00:47:05.811 --> 00:47:08.511
She said, “Now in my upkar  I’ve got it.”

00:47:08.511 --> 00:47:11.011
So I said, “You enjoy it now!”

00:47:12.665 --> 00:47:15.827
You have paid for it by doing upkar!

00:47:15.827 --> 00:47:25.024
Upkar is ... Upkar means in Hindi
.. doing it with our doing it

00:47:25.024 --> 00:47:31.304
You just do it, without doing it. You even do not know you are doing. It's so simple.  Alright?

00:47:31.304 --> 00:47:33.244
It becomes part of your inner religion.

00:47:33.244 --> 00:47:40.328
Yes, otherwise, you think you are doing something, that
means pride comes into you, and the whole thing is spoiled.

00:47:40.382 --> 00:47:45.401
But Mother, the more we surrender and the more
we have faith, the more it will be alright.

00:47:45.430 --> 00:47:51.551
Yes, it will be alright.You see, if you are alright, if
you are strong people, then the Virata becomes alright,

00:47:51.551 --> 00:47:56.951
the Primordial becomes alright,  if you become a strong body.

00:47:58.915 --> 00:48:01.415
If some part of the body is sick you can cure it.

00:48:03.155 --> 00:48:05.655
How many cells do you need to fight them? Not much.

00:48:14.515 --> 00:48:17.325
But we are the fighting
cells. We have to fight them.

00:48:17.325 --> 00:48:20.435
By not becoming identified with them.

00:48:20.455 --> 00:48:25.475
You see, you have to fight with them in
such a way that you do not weep for them.

00:48:25.511 --> 00:48:28.391
Means you are affected by them. No!

00:48:28.431 --> 00:48:30.931
You are detached.

00:48:30.931 --> 00:48:33.711
You just say, “You will be
alright,” and they will be alright.

00:48:33.711 --> 00:48:37.261
So much powers you
have! Do you know that?

00:48:37.301 --> 00:48:40.981
But once you start weeping for
them, the power is neutralised.

00:48:45.301 --> 00:48:49.291
It should be done without any guide, anything,
you just say, “Alright, you will be alright.”

00:48:49.291 --> 00:48:53.505
Which is all well and good. Otherwise
there is no question of prestige for us!

00:48:56.075 --> 00:49:08.213
If somebody is cured, well and good. We have
not taken everybody’s bond that we should do it.

00:49:09.983 --> 00:49:16.017
We’ll do if we want to. If we don’t want to we’ll
not do it. It’s in complete freedom that we do it.

00:49:16.017 --> 00:49:21.093
At least I do! It’s in absolute freedom,

00:49:21.107 --> 00:49:23.607
because if I want to do, I will
do; otherwise I will not do.

00:49:25.777 --> 00:49:28.277
In the same way you should be.

00:49:29.737 --> 00:49:38.918
So then the detachment comes you see. Complete freedom
is also complete detachment, and that is complete love.

00:49:38.978 --> 00:49:49.639
Sometimes Mother when I go to some place people say that they used to know me before feeling very much for them and showing it,

00:49:49.653 --> 00:49:56.613
and that, if through Sahaja Yoga you become
unfeeling…That’s how they interpret it, becoming unfeeling.

00:49:56.610 --> 00:50:01.083
Unfeeling? No you should say, “Now
I understand that what was lacking.

00:50:01.083 --> 00:50:04.283
And I have too much feeling for
you. You become Sahaja Yogis.”

00:50:04.283 --> 00:50:09.033
You see, they always depended on
you and you had to give them.

00:50:09.071 --> 00:50:12.983
Alright, now you should say,
“You also become givers now!

00:50:13.033 --> 00:50:15.976
Through Sahaja Yoga you
can become equal to me.

00:50:16.023 --> 00:50:18.296
I want you to become that.”

00:50:18.296 --> 00:50:24.216
You see, sitting down and weeping for somebody
is no good. And some people are like this also.

00:50:24.965 --> 00:50:26.826
They like the sympathy?

00:50:26.826 --> 00:50:29.326
You see, they  like the show of the thing.

00:50:32.506 --> 00:50:37.488
Say you go to a place and they say,
“Oh, have you seen? Is he with her?”

00:50:37.508 --> 00:50:40.419
All that should go away.

00:50:40.456 --> 00:50:47.159
Maria, for a person like me, I will just,
I may not even bother. Why should I?

00:50:47.187 --> 00:50:55.127
I’m not attached. But then, you see, people like it if
somebody comes and too much asks. That's not feeling!

00:50:55.147 --> 00:50:58.647
Feeling is when it is in pure detachment.

00:51:01.837 --> 00:51:07.861
You are not feelingless, you are not
emotionless, but you are emotion.

00:51:07.929 --> 00:51:10.429
You become the emotion.

00:51:15.760 --> 00:51:19.069
Emotion is identified with you completely.

00:51:19.134 --> 00:51:19.999
Do you understand?

00:51:20.039 --> 00:51:20.669
Yes

00:51:20.669 --> 00:51:23.169
You are the emotion.

00:51:23.239 --> 00:51:25.739
The complete ocean: ocean of emotion.

00:51:25.739 --> 00:51:27.589
You generate emotion!

00:51:27.589 --> 00:51:30.089
When you are with people they get into emotions.

00:51:30.089 --> 00:51:34.019
You can inspire emotions into them.

00:51:34.049 --> 00:51:39.406
But nobody’s emotion should affect
you, then only it is possible.

00:51:42.507 --> 00:51:46.286
Even the ocean cannot become like a pond.

00:51:46.336 --> 00:51:53.665
Do you remember Mother, in the letter, I wrote a
sentence that I have a little bit of a problem of work.

00:51:53.695 --> 00:51:55.895
This was the problem Mother.

00:51:55.895 --> 00:52:02.195
Although I put the people's names in a
bandhan and I would pray for them at home,

00:52:02.262 --> 00:52:07.535
at work I would be detached from their emotions and their problems

00:52:07.607 --> 00:52:14.952
and because of that they would be upset
why they could not attract my attention.

00:52:14.961 --> 00:52:20.322
You see, my attention was attracted but
not to the point to become part of it

00:52:20.349 --> 00:52:27.628
and that would upset them and that’s why I had the
problem because they sent very negative vibrations back

00:52:27.628 --> 00:52:33.187
which eventually I could not tolerate and feel..

00:52:33.218 --> 00:52:35.307
No, you should be tactful about it.

00:52:35.317 --> 00:52:38.807
You should be tactful. You should be tactful about them.

00:52:38.807 --> 00:52:45.807
That is not the thing. Only thing is, you see, even if you
bleed, it doesn’t matter as long as it doesn’t hurt you inside.

00:52:45.847 --> 00:52:48.347
If it’s all outside, it’s alright.

00:52:49.353 --> 00:52:55.273
Attention, when you give to somebody,
you should be fully attentive to yourself.

00:52:55.326 --> 00:53:01.413
But the attention Mother, that they needed
was a selfish one which I did not entertain.

00:53:01.413 --> 00:53:03.913
Don’t entertain them. You see,
what I am saying is that,

00:53:03.913 --> 00:53:11.003
as you are Realised you will be surprised that you are in
a different wavelength absolutely, on a different position.

00:53:11.033 --> 00:53:16.933
And it is going to be a little difficult to adjust
with others because they want you the same person.

00:53:16.984 --> 00:53:19.233
You cannot be the same. You are a different one.

00:53:19.259 --> 00:53:23.033
It was only that you could give them
something for the time being, that’s all.

00:53:23.130 --> 00:53:27.644
But now, they will know that you have curative
powers; you can cure them, you can do things.

00:53:27.690 --> 00:53:32.494
Your value will go up much more!

00:53:32.512 --> 00:53:36.414
So you need not try to worry about these things. Gradually they will accept you.

00:53:36.464 --> 00:53:38.964
Things have sorted themselves out.

00:53:38.964 --> 00:53:46.534
Yes, they will sort it out! There are thousands of people behind you! You don’t know there are chiranjeevas (eternal beings) there are great personalities behind you.

00:53:46.584 --> 00:53:49.084
So you just let go.

00:53:49.084 --> 00:53:56.568
And we are not to be guided by their norms, not by them. We
have to put our own norms because we are different people.

00:53:59.238 --> 00:54:03.268
But first have confidence in yourselves!  First thing!

00:54:11.403 --> 00:54:13.903
Are you better Atul now?

00:54:14.865 --> 00:54:18.245
Now, Simon how are you? Are you
feeling guilty about something?

00:54:18.705 --> 00:54:20.178
No.

00:54:22.476 --> 00:54:26.785
Now you don’t swing from one end to
another, just try to keep in the centre.

00:54:32.112 --> 00:54:37.528
You have read a lot and you know a lot,

00:54:37.561 --> 00:54:40.408
that’s called as dhyana. You have got dhyana.

00:54:40.506 --> 00:54:43.486
But you haven’t got bodha.

00:54:44.441 --> 00:54:45.406
Bodha.

00:54:45.406 --> 00:54:46.136
Oh Bodhi?

00:54:46.136 --> 00:54:47.966
Bodha

00:54:47.956 --> 00:54:53.256
Means your dhyana is not
enlightened as yet. Aright?

00:54:53.296 --> 00:55:00.557
Because one is ‘to know’, and the another is
‘to know that the knowledge is enlightened’.

00:55:00.604 --> 00:55:04.802
This is the difference
between the two. Alright?

00:55:04.802 --> 00:55:11.355
The other day Gavin asked me, “What is samadhi?”
So I told him, "It is enlightened awareness."

00:55:11.394 --> 00:55:17.305
Enlightened awareness. You are aware, but
you are not enlightened. Samadhi is that.

00:55:17.305 --> 00:55:25.914
So in Sahaja Yoga, first you get nirvichara samadhi
– that is thoughtless enlightened awareness.

00:55:25.964 --> 00:55:34.857
And secondly you get nirvikalpa samadhi –
that is doubtless enlightened awareness.

00:55:34.857 --> 00:55:40.731
So to go to doubtless condition
you must know to avoid doubts.

00:55:40.771 --> 00:55:44.407
You have to change your style of approach.

00:55:44.437 --> 00:55:50.017
You see, other things you might
have achieved through doubting,

00:55:50.037 --> 00:55:54.107
but Sahaja Yoga is achieved through resolve.

00:55:56.737 --> 00:55:59.300
You even have to pretend that
you don’t doubt to start with.

00:55:59.300 --> 00:56:05.897
You have to go on pretending with yourself. Tell your mind, “I
am not going to doubt.” Go on for a while. Then it works out.

00:56:05.897 --> 00:56:08.759
There’s nothing like the faith.

00:56:08.787 --> 00:56:11.287
Faith, I am saying, not
the blind faith but faith.

00:56:12.867 --> 00:56:17.659
You have got the vibrations
now. Now believe into them!

00:56:19.791 --> 00:56:22.052
That’s the only way!

00:56:24.522 --> 00:56:32.497
There’s no other way out I can tell you this much.
Those who have taken to doubting will never approach it.

00:56:34.316 --> 00:56:36.816
You’ll be thrown away all the time with doubts.

00:56:38.826 --> 00:56:42.776
And a time may come when my attention may
recede and you’ll drop out just like that.

00:56:42.818 --> 00:56:49.448
You just cannot do Sahaja Yoga like
that. But blind faith is not needed.

00:56:49.463 --> 00:56:51.553
First you feel the vibrations.

00:56:51.576 --> 00:56:53.918
You see for yourself.

00:56:53.988 --> 00:56:59.428
Either we absolutely have blind faith or we have
rationality. Can’t we be something in between?

00:57:02.863 --> 00:57:07.001
The people who are absolutely blind are useless.

00:57:07.045 --> 00:57:12.945
They might be saved because if they can ask questions to me
that, “Are you this? Are you that?” Then they can be saved.

00:57:12.945 --> 00:57:15.915
If they come to that point!

00:57:15.961 --> 00:57:20.145
But those who are rational, they can never come into it!

00:57:21.821 --> 00:57:29.527
Because it’s like jumping like a monkey, from one
branch to another branch. You can never land down.

00:57:31.020 --> 00:57:40.092
It’s only through faith, shraddha, through
surrendering, you are going to achieve that state.

00:57:45.022 --> 00:57:50.942
And then small ripples here and there,
nothing, is going to disturb you.

00:57:52.741 --> 00:58:08.032
You are going to enjoy that state within
yourself. Allow your faith to dissolve you.

00:58:08.071 --> 00:58:10.571
You know the time is very short.

00:58:10.571 --> 00:58:19.925
You’ve got your Realisation and you take so
much time after that to come up to that,

00:58:19.942 --> 00:58:23.955
and that time is very much lost. Why do it?

00:58:23.988 --> 00:58:30.262
Now you have seen people who have shraddha how
far they have gone, so why not follow them?

00:58:41.406 --> 00:58:43.906
So that is very important

00:58:43.906 --> 00:58:48.565
that, by doubting you are not
going to achieve anything!

00:58:51.564 --> 00:58:55.745
You’ll be tossing. But you are to really put…

00:58:55.849 --> 00:59:00.514
Big girls have gone out.

00:59:00.599 --> 00:59:05.054
The big girls have gone out to play, you
also go out and play with them, alright?

00:59:05.084 --> 00:59:05.944
OK.

00:59:05.954 --> 00:59:10.088
Alright. See, how confident!
Because they are innocent.

00:59:12.308 --> 00:59:15.288
They have faith in themselves.

00:59:18.350 --> 00:59:23.241
So stop your rationality. It is not going to take you anywhere!

00:59:30.141 --> 00:59:38.225
You have to learn to develop your shraddha. Even you get Realisation, you cure people, you do anything.

00:59:38.225 --> 00:59:40.725
We have an example of somebody you know of.

00:59:40.725 --> 00:59:48.484
His mother was cured just like that. He was cured just like
that. He got a job just like that. He got whatever he wanted,

00:59:48.534 --> 00:59:51.034
and then suddenly he drops out!

00:59:51.034 --> 00:59:53.534
Without any shraddha.

00:59:58.658 --> 01:00:01.158
So that is what it is.

01:00:05.258 --> 01:00:14.789
So many have done like that because if you do not have shraddha, you get tired of jumping from one to another.

01:00:14.849 --> 01:00:18.031
All the time you are doubting in
this. It’s just a mental feat.

01:00:18.031 --> 01:00:25.248
We like to do circus for a while, it’s alright, but forget it! Now jump into it and get it!

01:00:25.355 --> 01:00:27.855
Now what do you lose?

01:00:29.604 --> 01:00:32.104
You lose nothing!

01:00:32.954 --> 01:00:35.194
We lose ego.

01:00:35.220 --> 01:00:39.084
Ego. You lose your ego but you get your personality.

01:00:39.084 --> 01:00:42.584
What do you lose? Nothing.
You get all the powers.

01:00:43.716 --> 01:00:47.576
Now the time is too short and you
are taking too long to do it.

01:00:49.053 --> 01:00:55.896
And some of you will be tired, jumping like that all the time
with your doubts, this way, that way. And what are you doubting?

01:00:58.487 --> 01:01:00.987
It’s all free.

01:01:00.987 --> 01:01:05.325
You don’t have to do anything about it.

01:01:05.365 --> 01:01:07.865
And doubting people can be quite foolish.

01:01:07.865 --> 01:01:11.955
They doubt about every nonsensical
thing which has no meaning at all.

01:01:13.151 --> 01:01:16.829
They see things which do not exist

01:01:16.851 --> 01:01:25.911
because it’s just, you see, a habit, or you can say an indulgence; you can say an entertainment for people, to doubt into this. And then doubt.

01:01:25.975 --> 01:01:29.932
You see they are just jumping like monkeys.

01:01:29.992 --> 01:01:32.492
Stop that!

01:01:37.792 --> 01:01:47.259
Any one of you who goes down into shraddha and dissolves
becomes a great instrument in the hands of God!

01:01:53.611 --> 01:01:56.111
Even to say that, “I doubt,” is wrong.

01:01:58.080 --> 01:02:03.390
These people think we are very honest
by saying, “I doubt. I doubt Mother.”

01:02:03.410 --> 01:02:06.540
Please give up such ‘honesties’!

01:02:06.580 --> 01:02:09.620
It’s absurd!

01:02:09.647 --> 01:02:14.380
This is ego which is making you
say these things that, “I doubt.”

01:02:14.400 --> 01:02:20.526
Because by saying that, it exists and you feel you are very
honest. It’s not you are doubting, your ego is doubting.

01:02:25.109 --> 01:02:30.450
When you realise that, that your ego
is doubting, it will become easier.

01:02:31.670 --> 01:02:37.020
“It’s not I who is doubting,
it’s my ego which is doubting.

01:02:37.067 --> 01:02:40.210
Or maybe some possession
in me which is doubting.”

01:02:43.309 --> 01:02:47.960
“Am I playing into the hands of
some possession or my own ego?”

01:02:50.400 --> 01:02:52.900
That’s what it is – hundred percent!

01:02:54.880 --> 01:03:00.362
Because those who have not doubted have gone
too far. You have seen people in India.

01:03:00.372 --> 01:03:03.195
You have seen Dhumal.

01:03:03.195 --> 01:03:05.482
He never doubted!

01:03:05.482 --> 01:03:13.767
His own brother, he was helped so much: he had no money to eat his food, he had gone to that condition because he had put a lot of money in a business which was failing.

01:03:13.799 --> 01:03:17.467
When he came to Sahaja Yoga his business
started earning just like that.

01:03:17.520 --> 01:03:19.020
He became a moneyed man.

01:03:19.028 --> 01:03:25.670
His child was sick, he was cured. He was sick, he was cured.
His wife was sick with something incurable, she was cured.

01:03:25.670 --> 01:03:28.170
But still he was doubting.

01:03:30.260 --> 01:03:32.220
He started taking drinks after that.

01:03:32.243 --> 01:03:35.580
He never used to take drinks, after
doubting he started taking drinks.

01:03:35.580 --> 01:03:40.640
He did all that was prohibited in Sahaja Yoga just to prove his point.

01:03:40.700 --> 01:03:43.200
And where is he now?

01:03:46.920 --> 01:03:52.925
I would say, pay attention to
your Self and not to your doubts!

01:03:52.925 --> 01:03:58.666
The doubts are coming from some dark
corners of your mind which is with you.

01:03:58.725 --> 01:04:03.595
What are you going to lose is
the point you must look into.

01:04:03.635 --> 01:04:07.709
Sort it out there. What have others lost?

01:04:08.819 --> 01:04:11.319
They have gained.

01:04:12.549 --> 01:04:16.275
Those who have doubted have lost, lost time.

01:04:24.997 --> 01:04:29.647
So don’t waste your time in useless things.

01:04:32.152 --> 01:04:34.652
There’s nothing to doubt.

01:04:38.938 --> 01:04:43.680
Every word I say is
the truth and the truth.

01:04:47.770 --> 01:04:50.270
See the vibrations.

01:04:54.443 --> 01:04:58.140
You see! I have to boast.

01:04:58.140 --> 01:05:01.433
You see! Every word.

01:05:04.083 --> 01:05:06.583
So don’t doubt it!

01:05:06.583 --> 01:05:10.863
Just take it and take it and take it.

01:05:10.903 --> 01:05:14.401
I know all this myself.

01:05:14.423 --> 01:05:18.184
I am not going to achieve anything by telling you these things,

01:05:20.844 --> 01:05:29.241
except that you will know me and I will know you.

01:05:34.521 --> 01:05:39.831
You are not to lose anything. You have to gain.

01:05:39.866 --> 01:05:45.994
So tell your mind to shut up for a while! It
is already running with a very fast speed.

01:05:59.838 --> 01:06:06.758
We want to get to that state of complete
doubtless awareness and, for that,

01:06:06.782 --> 01:06:12.642
are we going to carry these
doubts in our pockets?

01:06:12.668 --> 01:06:20.242
They have no meaning. They will all be neutralised. You have
seen people who have neutralised it. But those who do it…

01:06:23.688 --> 01:06:26.188
I have no word.

01:06:35.103 --> 01:06:37.603
Steady your shraddha. Steady it!

01:06:37.603 --> 01:06:42.453
It’s a force. It’s like a flame of a candle.

01:06:42.453 --> 01:06:44.953
Steady it!

01:06:45.277 --> 01:06:56.988
But by your doubts you are putting heavy pressure
on it and the flame, it has to face those doubts.

01:06:57.878 --> 01:07:00.378
You are weakening yourself!

01:07:16.098 --> 01:07:20.350
Simon you have to get well. You are a seeker for ages now.

01:07:20.347 --> 01:07:25.759
In many lives you have been seeking. And now you
are not going to play about anymore. Alright?

01:07:25.857 --> 01:07:31.079
You are going to be a certain
(unclear) . Absolutely, alright?

01:07:31.077 --> 01:07:33.577
Mataji may I go now?

01:07:34.457 --> 01:07:35.589
Alright. You may go.

01:07:35.629 --> 01:07:38.489
See you

01:07:38.519 --> 01:07:42.149
And you throw those away and bring
seven more [lemons] to me in my house.

01:07:42.149 --> 01:07:43.249
Tomorrow night?

01:07:43.299 --> 01:07:44.709
Tomorrow night.

01:07:44.749 --> 01:07:47.249
What time would you like me to turn up?

01:07:47.249 --> 01:07:51.199
Oh, any time from about five
onwards, that’s better. Alright?

01:07:51.199 --> 01:07:57.839
Five, six, anytime. Come to my house, bring them. And ask
Philippa to come and see me also tomorrow evening, if possible,

01:07:57.892 --> 01:08:01.429
because I’ll talk to her about
this, what is to be given.

01:08:01.484 --> 01:08:03.984
Seven chillies as well as seven lemons?

01:08:04.021 --> 01:08:09.609
Yes, yes. Alright? And as I love you, try to
love yourself. And now don’t get after yourself.

01:09:33.318 --> 01:09:40.418
One more thing I would like to tell you, because
there's time today, I can tell you about these things.

01:09:40.468 --> 01:09:45.978
for certain chakras how to clear
them, even physically you can try.

01:09:46.017 --> 01:09:49.346
One of them is of Vishuddhi chakra.

01:09:49.392 --> 01:09:56.029
Now for Vishuddhi chakra, I have told you many things
but you can try one more thing which will help you.

01:09:56.045 --> 01:10:00.149
Is to put your head on the ground like this,

01:10:00.196 --> 01:10:04.709
near a bed, with your feet on the bed, resting on the bed.

01:10:04.753 --> 01:10:10.720
And try to come on the bed more and more,

01:10:11.953 --> 01:10:13.589
more and more.

01:10:13.620 --> 01:10:18.184
The body... push it on the bed so the whole pressure comes up here.

01:10:18.235 --> 01:10:21.744
Alright. And then keep my photograph handy.

01:10:21.777 --> 01:10:29.323
In that stage you see my photograph.
It will improve your Vishuddhis.

01:10:29.343 --> 01:10:32.832
In that case, in case you have Left Vishuddhi,

01:10:32.872 --> 01:10:38.392
then you turn your face towards the right and see it.

01:10:38.475 --> 01:10:42.831
If you have the Right Vishuddhi then turn
your face to the left and see my photograph.

01:10:42.880 --> 01:10:48.713
That will help you because all of you have
Vishuddhi problem. This will be of help.

01:10:48.735 --> 01:10:51.783
You mean the neck on the floor?

01:10:51.782 --> 01:10:54.282
On the floor if you lie down.

01:10:54.292 --> 01:11:03.802
Now just lie down now, facing that side
towards the…yes, now go ahead, like that.

01:11:03.821 --> 01:11:09.405
Gavin be careful. Now, go down. You go down, and more, more.

01:11:09.435 --> 01:11:13.345
Again try to bring this lower portion on top.

01:11:13.380 --> 01:11:15.880
Bring the body straight.

01:11:18.200 --> 01:11:21.860
Yes. So that there isn’t much of a Hatha Yoga.

01:11:21.925 --> 01:11:24.425
Can you see? Yes.

01:11:25.912 --> 01:11:32.576
Do you rest the weight on your shoulders
or the head? Pressure on the neck?

01:11:32.695 --> 01:11:37.750
More on the Vishuddhi. Better now?

01:11:38.726 --> 01:11:43.152
Where do you have the photo if you’re not going to look at it?

01:11:49.020 --> 01:11:52.016
No, no. You have the photo whichever side you look.

01:11:52.060 --> 01:11:55.238
Yeah, I know. But if you’re not going
to look to the left or the right?

01:11:55.268 --> 01:12:00.941
You turn your photograph with you. You must look at the
photograph isn’t it? Because it helps your Agnya, always.

01:12:00.971 --> 01:12:04.464
You see, if your Agnya is kept clear then
it should be cleared out better, that's why.

01:12:04.454 --> 01:12:06.954
You see that's why you have to have a photograph,

01:12:06.954 --> 01:12:12.886
because your Agnya can be cleared out with that. Otherwise the Agnya is blocked. You see? Better?

01:12:12.903 --> 01:12:13.746
Hmmm. It’s very good.

01:12:13.746 --> 01:12:16.246
Very good!

01:12:17.596 --> 01:12:19.916
All of you should try this thing.

01:12:19.916 --> 01:12:24.524
I have told you about, for Swadishthana,
what should be done. That you remember?

01:12:24.557 --> 01:12:25.714
Should I show them?

01:12:25.714 --> 01:12:29.874
Yes show them what is to be done
for Swadishthana – physically.

01:12:35.368 --> 01:12:37.868
And you say the mantra?

01:12:38.748 --> 01:12:41.701
Yes you can say the mantra,
would be a good idea.

01:12:42.400 --> 01:12:45.861
Now for people who have a problem of Mooladhara,

01:12:45.890 --> 01:12:55.977
or say those who cannot sit on the ground and sort of  thing:
for them, it’s to practice with both your legs like this.

01:12:56.007 --> 01:13:00.877
Put them like that, you too have the same problem.

01:13:00.877 --> 01:13:09.257
Put these two [feet] together like this. You see, you cannot stretch it much. Try to stretch it down (the knees) on to the ground!

01:13:09.287 --> 01:13:15.396
Try to, try to, as much as you can!
But, in one shot you cannot do it!

01:13:15.436 --> 01:13:16.768
You have to put your knees down?

01:13:16.820 --> 01:13:21.736
Yes. Put your knees down.
They must touch the ground.

01:13:21.770 --> 01:13:25.270
I can do perfectly, despite my fat!

01:13:29.684 --> 01:13:35.014
Try to raise it and push that down. Gradually you have to
do it. You’ll do it the bathroom, you will work it out.

01:13:35.014 --> 01:13:39.464
That’s very good. You lift this so
only your Mooladhara is touching.

01:13:45.984 --> 01:13:53.384
Try to put it further, further. Now try to do that -
further. That helps you see, that helps. Further up! No.

01:13:53.384 --> 01:14:01.544
No, no, put this together and move that! Just push that,
just feet. No, no feet! Spread  the feet .

01:14:01.584 --> 01:14:02.844
Feet apart.

01:14:02.872 --> 01:14:05.372
Now do as I tell you.

01:14:06.600 --> 01:14:07.990
Where do you live?

01:14:07.990 --> 01:14:10.490
Wiltshire.

01:14:10.490 --> 01:14:13.799
Spread much more. Spread it much more

01:14:15.906 --> 01:14:18.406
That helps you see. That helps.

01:14:20.460 --> 01:14:22.960
First you do this exercise.

01:14:34.490 --> 01:14:36.990
It’s working out. It’s much better now.

01:14:43.887 --> 01:14:47.797
Gradually, you will see it will work
out, gradually. It's better now.

01:14:47.812 --> 01:14:50.602
You see gradually it will work out, gradually, if you do it.

01:14:50.602 --> 01:14:55.829
It’s good for Mooladhara. For all the people who
have mooladhara problem, this would be a good idea.

01:14:55.909 --> 01:14:58.959
So gradually we should see to different chakras.

01:15:00.449 --> 01:15:01.989
Now for the Hamsa.

01:15:02.008 --> 01:15:02.939
Which Chakra?

01:15:02.969 --> 01:15:05.297
Hamsa!

01:15:05.337 --> 01:15:11.697
You lie on your body like that on your stomach.

01:15:15.538 --> 01:15:16.857
Now come along!

01:15:16.857 --> 01:15:23.017
Put your these things, Mooladharas, here on the Hamsa,

01:15:23.037 --> 01:15:26.824
and now ask the Mother Earth to suck in your problems.

01:15:29.401 --> 01:15:32.190
But the pressure should be quite a lot on that.

01:15:45.473 --> 01:15:47.973
Now you move it.

01:15:57.913 --> 01:16:04.183
Better? You feel better? You can feel the
sensation at the bottom. Allow them to disappear.

01:16:07.870 --> 01:16:11.952
Here, even your pressure will go away from your…

01:16:12.006 --> 01:16:14.506
You’ll feel relieved from the pressure.
